headline.main: Ohio Vet Shoots at Firefighters, Thinking It Was a Break-In
headline.print_headline: Ohio Vet Shoots at Firefighters, Thinking It Was a Break-In

lead_paragraph: Police say a veteran who shot at firefighters conducting a welfare check at his Cincinnati home won't be charged in connection with the misunderstanding.
